    Process
    public class PatchProcessInflammationCD8
extends PatchProcessInflammation
    Extension of PatchProcessInflammation for CD8 CAR T-cells

    InflammationCD8 determines granzyme amounts produced for cytotoxic effector functions as a function of IL-2 bound and antigen-induced activation state.
